gory:Lists of war films]]\n[[Category:Lists of films by setting]]\n[[Category:Films based on the Bangladesh Liberation War]]\n[[Category:Indian war films]]\n", "name_user": "Sid95Q", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eIndia", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_films_about_1971_India-Pakistan_war"}
